Yup, I know. He came to like right before BrightBlade was slagged and 
captured, so I'd be surprised if he did no anything.

::Kluster::

Kluster nods, walking to the cell. He kneels down, picking up 
Gangon's remains. The slightly sickened look was obvious on Kluster's 
face.

He carrues Gangon to the next room, motioning for Ice and Gangon to 
follow. Putting Gangon's head in the space provided on the console, 
Kluster begins the scan. A proccess indicator quickly begins counting 
toward 100%.
